      • randomElement

        public static <E> E randomElement(java.util.Collection<E> col)
        Returns a random element from the given iterable. Useful for getting random element from non-indexed collections, like HashSets.

        Synchronizes on the given col to prevent concurrent modification. Returns null if col is null or empty.
